patthana16.93:1.1: Anidassanaappaṭighaṃ niyataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca naanidassanaappaṭigho naniyato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (Saṃkhittaṃ.) Hetuyā cha, adhipatiyā cha …pe… avigate cha.
patthana16.93:2.1: Anidassanaappaṭighaṃ aniyataṃ dhammaṃ paccayā nasanidassanasappaṭigho naaniyato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (Saṃkhittaṃ.) Hetuyā tīṇi …pe… avigate tīṇi.
